l-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tai-sao-nen-quang-cao-bang-am-thanh-lap-ke-hoach-quang-cao-am-thanh.html\/#Tai_sao_quang_bang_am_thanh_lai_quan_trong\" title=\"T\u1ea1i sao qu\u1ea3ng b\u1eb1ng \u00e2m thanh l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng?\">T\u1ea1i sao qu\u1ea3ng b\u1eb1ng \u00e2m thanh l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tai-sao-nen-quang-cao-bang-am-thanh-lap-ke-hoach-quang-cao-am-thanh.html\/#Loi_ich_cua_quang_cao_am_thanh_ky_thuat_so\" title=\"L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1\">L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tai-sao-nen-quang-cao-bang-am-thanh-lap-ke-hoach-quang-cao-am-thanh.html\/#Quang_cao_am_thanh_co_pham_vi_tiep_can_rong_rai\" title=\"Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tai-sao-nen-quang-cao-bang-am-thanh-lap-ke-hoach-quang-cao-am-thanh.html\/#Quang_cao_am_thanh_co_the_tuong_tac\" title=\"Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tai-sao-nen-quang-cao-bang-am-thanh-lap-ke-hoach-quang-cao-am-thanh.html\/#Tao_chien_luoc_quang_cao_am_thanh\" title=\"T\u1ea1o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh\">T\u1ea1o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tai-sao-nen-quang-cao-bang-am-thanh-lap-ke-hoach-quang-cao-am-thanh.html\/#Quyet_dinh_kenh\" title=\"Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00eanh\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00eanh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tai-sao-nen-quang-cao-bang-am-thanh-lap-ke-hoach-quang-cao-am-thanh.html\/#Biet_khan_gia_cua_ban\" title=\"Bi\u1ebft kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n\">Bi\u1ebft kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tai-sao-nen-quang-cao-bang-am-thanh-lap-ke-hoach-quang-cao-am-thanh.html\/#Xem_xet_ket_qua\" title=\"Xem x\u00e9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3\">Xem x\u00e9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u00edch h\u1ee3p qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0o tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u00e2m thanh nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t nh\u1ea1c tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn ho\u1eb7c podcast c\u00f3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecd.<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"heading align-start color-normal heading-size--normal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_sao_quang_bang_am_thanh_lai_quan_trong\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ea1i sao qu\u1ea3ng b\u1eb1ng \u00e2m thanh l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb b\u1eb1ng \u00e2m thanh.\u00a0Ngo\u00e0i \u00e2m thanh truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qua radio,\u00a0\u00e2m thanh ph\u00e1t tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng 64% k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho ph\u00e9p ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng, s\u00e1ch n\u00f3i, phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u00e2m thanh c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i \u0111\u0103ng blog ho\u1eb7c podcast.\u00a0V\u00ed d\u1ee5, eMarketer ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra r\u1eb1ng\u00a060% ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh \u1edf M\u1ef9 t\u1eeb 18 \u0111\u1ebfn 34 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi nghe podcast h\u00e0ng th\u00e1ng.<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"heading align-start color-normal heading-size--normal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Loi_ich_cua_quang_cao_am_thanh_ky_thuat_so\"><\/span><strong>L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi t\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed9i dung k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1. V\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t loa th\u00f4ng minh trong 41% h\u1ed9 gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u1edf Hoa K\u1ef3. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u1edf n\u01a1i h\u1ecd \u0111ang nghe n\u1ed9i dung cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u1edf c\u00e1c th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c nhau trong ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 trong c\u00e1c b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 trong nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ho\u1eb7c trong n\u1ed9i dung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, gi\u00fap thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 theo nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quang_cao_am_thanh_co_pham_vi_tiep_can_rong_rai\"><\/span>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh l\u00e0 ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c lu\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea1c v\u00e0 tin t\u1ee9c.<\/p>\n<div id=\"\" class=\"container     padding-bottom-xmini a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<h3 class=\"heading align-start color-normal heading-size--small\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quang_cao_am_thanh_co_the_tuong_tac\"><\/span>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"\" class=\"container     a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<p class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh.\u00a0V\u00ed d\u1ee5:<a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Loa_th%C3%B4ng_minh\"> loa th\u00f4ng minh<\/a> c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho ph\u00e9p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua h\u00e0ng r\u1ea3nh tay ho\u1eb7c podcast c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3\u00a0qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef\u00a0\u0111i k\u00e8m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5p trong \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng.\u00a0B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 trong c\u00e1c b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 theo nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<div id=\"1\" class=\"container     padding-bottom-mini a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<div>\n<h2 class=\"heading align-start color-normal heading-size--normal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tao_chien_luoc_quang_cao_am_thanh\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ea1o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"\" class=\"container     a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<p class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd khi t\u1ea1o \u00e2m thanh cho chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n . Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u k\u00eanh kh\u00e1c nhau, v\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u00ean bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch\u00a0 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u1edf \u0111\u00fang n\u01a1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nghe \u0111\u00f3. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, vi\u1ec7c \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch \u00e2m thanh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<figure style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/images.unsplash.com\/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&amp;ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=1000&amp;q=80\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m b\u00fat ch\u00ec g\u1ea7n m\u00e1y t\u00ednh x\u00e1ch tay\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"\" class=\"container     a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<h3 class=\"heading align-start color-normal heading-size--normal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quyet_dinh_kenh\"><\/span>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00eanh<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"\" class=\"container     a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<p class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">C\u1ea7n tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1eb9p ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n?\u00a0\u0110\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, h\u00e3y c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean loa th\u00f4ng minh l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t nh\u1ea1c tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn<\/p>\n<div id=\"\" class=\"container     padding-top-small a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<h3 class=\"heading align-start color-normal heading-size--normal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Biet_khan_gia_cua_ban\"><\/span>Bi\u1ebft kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"\" class=\"container     a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<p class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">H\u00e3y ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng g\u00ec kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm, nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd th\u00edch th\u00fa nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i dung \u00e2m thanh bao g\u1ed3m<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">c\u1ea3 ti\u1ebfng leng keng,<\/li>\n<li class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">\u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 v\u00e0<\/li>\n<li class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">n\u1ed9i dung c\u00f3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i.<\/p>\n<div id=\"\" class=\"container     padding-top-small a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<h3 class=\"heading align-start color-normal heading-size--normal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Xem_xet_ket_qua\"><\/span>Xem x\u00e9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"\" class=\"container     a20m border-type-none background-color-transparent desktop\">\n<p class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">\u00c2m thanh ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p . \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1eefu \u00edch. C\u00e1c ph\u00e9p \u0111o v\u1ec1<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">ph\u1ea1m vi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn<\/li>\n<li class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t<\/li>\n<li class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u00e2m thanh<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"text align-start color-normal text--word-break--normal text-size--normal\">l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ecdc th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/phim-long-tieng-nam-2022-theo-xu-huong-phat-trien.html\/\">Phim l\u1ed3ng ti\u1ebfng n\u0103m 2022 theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u00edch h\u1ee3p qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0o tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u00e2m thanh nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t nh\u1ea1c tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn ho\u1eb7c podcast c\u00f3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":14945,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[70],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u1eb1ng \u00e2m thanh, l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh - \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media Digital Marketing<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e2m thanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u00edch h\u1ee3p qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0o tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u00e2m thanh nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t nh\u1ea1c\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<li